FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine AS builder

WORKDIR /build

COPY pom.xml .
RUN apk add --no-cache maven && \
    mvn dependency:resolve && \
    rm -rf /root/.m2/repository/*/maven-metadata-local.xml

COPY src ./src
RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests && \
    mv target/*.jar app.jar

FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine

LABEL maintainer="analytics-team" \
      description="Java analytics dashboard" \
      version="1.0"

WORKDIR /app

RUN apk add --no-cache \
      fontconfig \
      ttf-dejavu \
      curl \
      ca-certificates && \
    rm -rf /var/cache/apk/*

RUN wget -O /tmp/rds-ca.pem https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/rds-ca-2019-root.pem && \
    wget -O /tmp/azure-ca.crt https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootCA.crt && \
    keytool -import -alias aws-rds-ca -file /tmp/rds-ca.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    keytool -import -alias azure-digicert -file /tmp/azure-ca.crt -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    rm -f /tmp/rds-ca.pem /tmp/azure-ca.crt

RUN addgroup -S -g 1001 app && \
    adduser -S -u 1001 -G app app

COPY --from=builder --chown=app:app /build/app.jar .

USER app

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

ENTRYPOINT ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
